    "class CustomBERTModel(BertForSequenceClassification):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, config):\n",
    "        super(CustomBERTModel, self).__init__(config)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 可以在这里修改 BERT 的一些结构，例如添加 Dropout 层、线性层等\n",
    "        self.dropout = nn.Dropout(0.3)  # 在 BERT 输出后加 Dropout\n",
    "        self.classifier = nn.Linear(config.hidden_size, 2)  # 线性层，输出 2 个类别\n",
    "\n",
    "    def forward(self, input_ids, attention_mask=None, labels=None):\n",
    "        outputs = self.bert(input_ids, attention_mask=attention_mask)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 取 [CLS] token 的表示作为分类的输入\n",
    "        pooled_output = outputs.pooler_output  # shape: [batch_size, hidden_size]\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 添加 Dropout 层\n",
    "        pooled_output = self.dropout(pooled_output)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 通过线性层进行分类\n",
    "        logits = self.classifier(pooled_output)  # shape: [batch_size, 2]\n",
    "\n",
    "        loss = None\n",
    "        if labels is not None:\n",
    "            loss_fct = nn.CrossEntropyLoss()\n",
    "            loss = loss_fct(logits.view(-1, 2), labels.view(-1))\n",
    "\n",
    "        return (loss, logits) if loss is not None else (logits,)"
   ]

    "class CustomDataset(Dataset):\n",
    "    def __init__(self, texts, labels, tokenizer, max_len=512):\n",
    "        self.texts = texts\n",
    "        self.labels = labels\n",
    "        self.tokenizer = tokenizer\n",
    "        self.max_len = max_len\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __len__(self):\n",
    "        return len(self.texts)\n",
    "\n",
    "    def __getitem__(self, item):\n",
    "        text = self.texts[item]\n",
    "        label = self.labels[item]\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 使用BERT tokenizer对文本进行编码\n",
    "        encoding = self.tokenizer.encode_plus(\n",
    "            text,\n",
    "            add_special_tokens=True,\n",
    "            max_length=self.max_len,\n",
    "            padding='max_length',\n",
    "            truncation=True,\n",
    "            return_attention_mask=True,\n",
    "            return_tensors='pt'\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return {\n",
    "            'input_ids': encoding['input_ids'].flatten(),\n",
    "            'attention_mask': encoding['attention_mask'].flatten(),\n",
    "            'label': torch.tensor(label, dtype=torch.long)\n",
    "        }\n"
   ]

    "def train_epoch(model, data_loader, optimizer, loss_fn, device, scheduler=None):\n",
    "    model = model.train()\n",
    "    losses = []\n",
    "    correct_predictions = 0\n",
    "\n",
    "    for batch in tqdm(data_loader, desc=\"Training\", leave=False):\n",
    "        input_ids = batch['input_ids'].to(device)\n",
    "        attention_mask = batch['attention_mask'].to(device)\n",
    "        labels = batch['label'].to(device)\n",
    "\n",
    "        optimizer.zero_grad()\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 前向传播\n",
    "        outputs = model(input_ids, attention_mask=attention_mask, labels=labels)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # 修改：outputs 是一个元组, loss 在 outputs[0] 中，logits 在 outputs[1] 中\n",
    "        loss = outputs[0]  # 损失值\n",
    "        logits = outputs[1]  # 预测值\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 反向传播\n",
    "        loss.backward()\n",
    "        optimizer.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 如果使用了学习率调度器\n",
    "        if scheduler:\n",
    "            scheduler.step()\n",
    "\n",
    "        losses.append(loss.item())\n",
    "\n",
    "        # 计算准确率\n",
    "        preds = torch.argmax(logits, dim=1)\n",
    "        correct_predictions += torch.sum(preds == labels)\n",
    "\n",
    "    avg_loss = torch.tensor(losses).mean().item()\n",
    "    accuracy = correct_predictions.double() / len(data_loader.dataset)\n",
    "\n",
    "    return avg_loss, accuracy\n"
   ]

    "import numpy as np\n",
    "def test_model(model, data_loader, device):\n",
    "    model = model.eval()  # 设置为评估模式\n",
    "    predictions = []\n",
    "    labels = []\n",
    "\n",
    "    with torch.no_grad():  # 不计算梯度\n",
    "        for batch in tqdm(data_loader, desc=\"Testing\"):\n",
    "            input_ids = batch['input_ids'].to(device)\n",
    "            attention_mask = batch['attention_mask'].to(device)\n",
    "            label = batch['label'].to(device)\n",
    "\n",
    "            # 前向传播\n",
    "            outputs = model(input_ids, attention_mask=attention_mask)\n",
    "            \n",
    "            # 如果是SequenceClassifierOutput，使用 .logits 获取预测结果\n",
